Package io.github.eutro.wasm2j.util

Class InsnMap<T>

java.lang.Object
io.github.eutro.wasm2j.util.InsnMap<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of value in the map.
public class InsnMap<T> extends Object
A map from WebAssembly opcodes to values.

Values should not be null.
